Dear {!Booking__r.Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!!

We would like to inform you that your Relationship Manager has been updated. Please find the details below for your reference:

Project: {!RW_Project__r.Name}
Unit Number: {Name}
New Relationship Manager: {!Relationship_Manager__r.Name}
Contact Number: {!Relationship_Manager__r.Contact_Number__c}
Email ID: {!Relationship_Manager__r.RM_Email__c}

Your new Relationship Manager will be your primary point of contact for any assistance regarding your unit, payments, documentation, or service requests.

Should you have any queries or require support, please feel free to reach out to your Relationship Manager directly.

Thank you for your continued trust in Runwal Enterprises.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
